</style><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://twitter.com/liberty030328/status/1698635745098182952" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc85jMCeRNWFdXesS_XBZi210ZXPwr-DbZr7UfCyroLqc0u0-d1oLI8_IGvAN0DbDz0zDCgBgkEmmCXyG3X8grOaUqLbJ_7Vv9hY50Tf7TcMgkiK95-UBrZZ9KL9B04n4xIXWVaVfLMnu2PVRFVnrwqf=w1097-h1672-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><p>此外，Tennen Sui 发推文（帖子）称，“<em>这就是为什么我不想谈论 Holorith 地区的原因。我发推文时并没有考虑到这一点</em><em>。</em> ”也明确表示这件事是真实发生的，无意因此而贬低Hololive Production的观众和粉丝。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/liberty030328/status/1698704007202828406" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc-o0wZ12SlmMqOIKxA34hbjE9uWI4_mEpFdFV8P04bx4cUVoroCnS6KSNP3RBh_OUwPuMyuDzDAN9u2QKmR4fCll--RAk6T-ZhRe7IxxIPjPCbPyLHV6tiLSPflMlyxXPTXclSWkDC9wi5VP-B2ecEj=w1097-h609-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><p>近年来，Hololive Production 的观众和粉丝无论性别都在增加，据报道，许多人正在参观各地举办的活动。</p><p>天年水的警告内容明确表明，随着活动参观人数的增加，存在不受欢迎的人混入的风险，可以说这是应该面对的事情。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="wn1nu5Ea6D"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-hololive-production-event-hololive-city-follow-up-release/">VTuber Office Hololive制作活动“Holo Live City”发布</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Office Hololive制作活动“Holo Live City”发布” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-hololive-production-event-hololive-city-follow-up-release/embed/#?secret=FYzhUGEsIR#?secret=wn1nu5Ea6D" data-secret="wn1nu5Ea6D" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://hololivecity.hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">全息城市</a></p><cite>全息直播制作</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“No.2（暂定）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙VTuber信息）</p><p></p><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/a-woman-who-was-molested-etc-at-vtuber-event-hololive-city-publishes-a-tweet-post-alerting-the-public-to-situation/">VTuber 事件后 一名在 Hololive City 被猥亵的女性发布了一条推文（帖子）以提醒她</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/a-woman-who-was-molested-etc-at-vtuber-event-hololive-city-publishes-a-tweet-post-alerting-the-public-to-situation/feed/ 0 100465
